thread.title_full: Omni Financial reviewed by Diane irons

author: Diane irons
title: Diane irons
text: Doing business with a group of professionals was a pleasure. From day one, the team was continually in contact with me to advise and consult me every step of the way. Sandy Mitchell gave 100 percent and was always supportive through this journey. This process takes time , but , I was confident that it would be worth it in the end. Thank you Sandy and all your elves for all your hard work and dedication. I am pleased to say that this is a very upstanding company and I would surely recommend Omni to anyone in a financial difficulties.
